{"article_id":"LUzufQsm1AxmsS67","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Obama Team","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"To Make Important ,","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"If Symbolic ,","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"Choice On Gay Marriage","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"The Obama administration faces tricky political and legal questions on the subject of gay marriage .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"By the end of this month , the federal government is expected to file not just one but two briefs in a pair of same-sex marriage cases at the U.S. Supreme Court .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"But it is the Proposition 8 case from California that poses the thornier questions for the administration","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"- questions so difficult","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"that the president himself is expected to make the final decision on what arguments","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"the Justice Department will make in the Supreme Court .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"Prop 8 ,","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"as it is known ,","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"is the California ballot initiative","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"banning same-sex marriage .","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"It was narrowly approved by state voters in 2008 .","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"A federal district court struck down the law as unconstitutional discrimination in 2010 .","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"A federal appeals court later agreed , but on narrower grounds .","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"Because there was a period of time","depth":14},{"id":18,"text":"in which same-sex couples could legally marry in California ,","depth":14},{"id":19,"text":"the court said ,","depth":13},{"id":20,"text":"it was unconstitutional for the state , through the ballot initiative , to take away a fundamental right","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"it had previously granted .","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"The state , under both Republican and Democratic governors , has declined to defend the measure in court .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"So its ban on gay marriage is being defended by the sponsors of the initiative .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"The Obama administration is not required to file any brief in the case","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"because it does not directly involve federal law .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"But administration sources say","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"the government will file a brief .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"Still unresolved is what the brief will say .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"And in this case , much more than most , there are numerous legal routes","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"that the government can take .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"The ultimate question","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"- the one","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"perhaps most people want an answer to","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"but may not get -","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"is whether same-sex couples have a constitutional right","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"to marry .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"A Supreme Court decision","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"that says yes to that","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"would invalidate laws in some 30 states .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"But there are many legal avenues short of such a far-reaching argument","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"that would invalidate Proposition 8 in California","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"and leave laws in other states intact .","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"What makes this even dicier is that President Obama has changed his position , seemingly a lot , over the past eight months .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"In May , in an ABC interview , he for the first time endorsed same-sex marriage from a personal point of view ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"but he went on to say","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"that the decision","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"on legalizing gay marriage","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"should be left to the states ,","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"where marriage matters are traditionally governed .","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"`` It is important for me to go ahead","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"and affirm","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"that I think","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"same-sex couples should be able to get married .","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"And I continue to believe","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"that this is an issue","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"that is going to be worked out at the local level ,","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"because historically this has not been a federal issue , ''","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"But eight months later at his inauguration , the president seemed to take a more expansive view .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"`` Our journey is not complete","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"until our gay brothers and sisters are treated like anyone else under the law .","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"For","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"if we are truly created equal ,","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"then surely the love","depth":15},{"id":65,"text":"we commit to one another","depth":15},{"id":66,"text":"must be equal as well , ''","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"Obama said .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"That language suggests","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"the president believes in a more basic constitutional right","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"to marry ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"analogous to the right","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"enunciated in a unanimous 1967 Supreme Court ruling","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"that struck down laws","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"barring interracial marriage .","depth":14},{"id":75,"text":"In that case , ironically , the federal government took no position in the Supreme Court .","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"So what will Obama do","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"now that he faces similar questions in a case about sexual orientation , not race ?","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"His administration could make a bold , full-throated defense of the right","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"to marry ,","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"an argument","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"that Obama seemed to suggest at his inaugural .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"Or it could argue a number of lesser positions :","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"That California ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"having extended the right","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"to marry to gay couples for a window of time ,","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"could not revoke the right .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"Or that California , like some other states , has a law","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"extending all rights to same-sex couples , except the right","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"to marry ,","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"and that such a distinction amounts to discrimination .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"Or it could argue","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"since the state is not defending the law ,","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"the case does not belong in court at all -","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"that the sponsors of the initiative have no legal standing in court .","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"For the gay community , and for those","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"advocating traditional marriage between a man and a woman , the position","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"the government takes in this case","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"is hugely important","depth":5},{"id":100,"text":"- if nothing else , as a symbol .","depth":4},{"id":101,"text":"Both sides have made formal presentations at the Justice Department","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"urging the administration to take their side .","depth":5},{"id":103,"text":"But the deadline has already passed for a brief","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"siding with Proposition 8 supporters ,","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"leaving only the question of what a brief on the other side will say .","depth":5},{"id":106,"text":"Same-sex marriage advocates are holding their collective breath for now","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"and maintaining a pretty studied public silence ,","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"hoping to avoid the impression","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"that the gay community is pressuring the administration .","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"Still , lawyers","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"who argue regularly before the court","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"are not so sure","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"that the administration 's brief ,","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"whatever it says ,","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"will make a big difference to the justices .","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"`` I 'm never going to tell you","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"that the solicitor general 's position does n't matter , ''","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"says former Bush administration Solicitor General Paul Clement .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"But in this case ,","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"he says ,","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"`` I think","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"it matters less . ''","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"Clement was hired by the House Republican leadership","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"to defend the constitutionality of the Defense of Marriage Act , or DOMA , in a case","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"that is paired with the Proposition 8 case in the Supreme Court .","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"The reason","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"he thinks","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"the administration 's brief in the Proposition 8 case matters less ,","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"he says ,","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"is `` because we already know","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"what their position is on DOMA","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"and one can extrapolate . ''","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"In the DOMA case , the Obama administration argues","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"that the federal law is unconstitutional","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"because it bars federal benefits to legally married same-sex couples -","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"benefits","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"that go automatically to legally married heterosexual couples .","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"Supreme Court advocate Tom Goldstein , founder of SCOTUSblog , makes a different point","depth":6},{"id":139,"text":"-","depth":7},{"id":140,"text":"that sometimes Supreme Court briefs are aimed at more than one audience .","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"He notes","depth":6},{"id":142,"text":"that in a truly historic case like this one , `` I think","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"part of what 's going on ... is a statement about what is morally right and wrong .","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"And so I think","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"it could matter to Americans much more","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"than it matters to the Supreme Court . ''","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":293,"left":150,"right":292,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":150,"left":0,"right":149,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":148,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":148,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":292,"left":246,"right":291,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":241,"right":245,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":188,"right":240,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":188,"left":155,"right":187,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":4,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":5,"right":153,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":6,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":7,"right":151,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":173,"right":186,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":173,"left":168,"right":172,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":168,"left":166,"right":167,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":158,"r